              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "item": "outpost_key_1",
                "place": "cave"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 4,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "cave",
                "to": "village"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 5,
              "action": "UNLOCK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "key_item": "outpost_key_1",
                "target_place": "outpost1"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 6,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost1",
                "to": "outpost2"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 7,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "viktor",
                "place": "outpost2",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "viktor",
                    "line": "You tread on ground you do not own. Turn back, or be removed."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "I'm not here to fight. I'm here to understand who's really running this island."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "viktor",
                    "line": "Order requires a strong hand. I provide that. Your curiosity is a liability."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Is it? Or is it just that you're afraid of what you'll find if you look behind the curtain?"
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "viktor",
                    "line": "There is no curtain. Only the truth of survival. Leave."
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 8,
              "action": "MOVE",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "from": "outpost2",
                "to": "outpost3"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 9,
              "action": "PICKUP",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "item": "toolkit_1",
                "place": "outpost3"
              }
            },
            {
              "step": 10,
              "action": "TALK",
              "actor": "player",
              "parameters": {
                "target": "the_doctor",
                "place": "outpost3",
                "dialogue_content": [
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "An uninvited variable. How... statistically inconvenient."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "Viktor thinks he's in charge. But I see your notes. You're the one pulling the strings."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "Viktor manages the chaos. I manage the science. We serve different masters, though you would struggle to comprehend the distinction."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "You're experimenting on the survivors. That's why the infection spreads."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "Evolution requires sacrifice. Do not mistake my precision for malice. It is merely efficiency."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "PLAYER",
                    "line": "I'm going to stop you. And I'm going to expose this."
                  },
                  {
                    "speaker": "the_doctor",
                    "line": "You lack the data to prove anything. And now, you lack the time."
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "quest_id": "Q2_2",
          "quest_title": "Securing the Escape Route",
          "steps": [
